description:
**OWASP Member Benefits**

* Professional network of experts
* Job channel
* Cutting edge projects
* Google WorkSpace (GSuite) account
* [Membership Portal](https://members.owasp.org/)
* Discounts on participating in OWASP events and training
* A vote in our OWASP Global Board elections
* Meaningful volunteer opportunities

**Membership Partnership Benefits\***

* Application-layer encryption made simple and sponsored by Ubiq (Coming Soon)
* Free access to an application security posture platform with AppSecPhoenix [Community Edition](https://appsecphoenix.cloud/signup/owasp)
* Core Concepts training and certification sponsored by [Security Journey](https://owasp.securityjourney.com/)
* Hands-on application security training through the [SecureFlag Platform](https://www.secureflag.com/owasp.html)

**[Click to become an OWASP Member.](https://owasp.org/membership/)**
\*Subject to change
title: Are you an OWASP Member?
